<p>If you are planning to make a transaction in your taxable account, it may sometimes be worth delaying the transaction slightly in order to reduce taxes.  (Do not wait a long time for the tax-optimal date; any tax saving may be lost in the cost of having the wrong portfolio for too long.)  This page summarizes some of the most common issues.
</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc"><tr><td><div id="toctitle"><h2>Contents</h2></div>
